sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User/Frontend
    participant B as Backend
    participant R as Redis
    participant A as Agent Worker
    participant M as MCP Servers
    participant L as LiteLLM/GPT-5.4

    U->>B: POST /conversations/{id}/messages
    B->>B: Save user message to Supabase
    B->>B: Create agent_tasks row (running)
    B->>R: LPUSH agent:tasks {task}
    B-->>U: 202 Accepted

    Note over U,B: Frontend opens WebSocket
    U->>B: WS /ws/conversations/{id}
    B->>R: SUBSCRIBE agent:status:{conv_id}

    A->>R: BLMOVE agent:tasks agent:processing
    R-->>A: {task payload}

    loop Agent processing
        A->>M: MCP tool call (HTTP+SSE)
        M-->>A: tool result
        A->>R: PUBLISH status update
        R-->>B: status update
        B->>B: Update agent_tasks.current_status
        B-->>U: WS push status text
        A->>L: LLM query (with base64 vision)
        L-->>A: LLM response
    end

    A->>R: PUBLISH final result
    A->>R: LREM agent:processing {task}
    R-->>B: result
    B->>B: Save to messages + agent_tasks=completed
    B-->>U: WS push final JSON
